'''Tiirarka Kacbada''' waxaa loola jeedaa waa afarta xagal ee [[Kacbada]]. waxaana loogu magacaabay mar in laga wado afarta jiho ee xigaan marna macno u gaar ah oo loola jeedo<ref>http://www.manhal.net/articles.php?action=show&id=16837</ref>
